Filmed over the course of 5 months in Scotland's 3 largest cities - Edinburgh, Glasgow and Aberdeen, Strippers is a new 3-part series that meets dancers and club owners, punters hell bent on having a good time

Strippers.[UK].s01e01.Glasgow.360p.LDTV.ABC.AU.WEBRIP.[MPup]

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/12/11/4eaec0a214c224993dc51c4bd92b1320.png[/img]

Strippers is a documentary series that takes a look at strip clubs which have doubled over the last 10 years with more and more young British women are turning to lap dancing to try and make a living. 

Episode 1: The cameras are in Glasgow, at strip-club called Diamond Dolls and it employs over 40 dancers.

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/12/11/fcb02712b6ecc8b52f6cfc5c730c3f61.jpg[/img]


Strippers.[UK].s01e02.Edinburgh.360p.LDTV.ABC.AU.WEBRIP.[MPup]

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/12/11/b3ec28324a781a193f393d35c9c00987.png[/img]

Episode 2: The cameras are in Edinburgh, which is home to three lap-dancing bars,in an area known as the Pubic Triangle. Charley is attempting to worker as a stripper at the same time as studying for a college degree. Vivi strips to try and make ends meet whilst Cuban Barbara has managed to earn up to Â£4000 per night.

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/12/11/e6ae5006e6d9438829d841de6ba91546.jpg[/img]


Strippers.[UK].s01e03.Aberdeen.360p.LDTV.ABC.AU.WEBRIP.[MPup]

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/12/13/9cac8fec0e76f032c47270e9164064eb.png[/img]

Episode 3: Aberdeen is currently Scotland's wealthiest city, and Vicky started stripping there as soon as she turned 18 and is addicted to the lifestyle. Lilly uses stripping as a stepping stone to her dream career as a Page 3 girl whilst touring strippers Danni and Xena travel the world dancing to fund Danni's MA in Art and Xena's love of adventure.
